Google tasks does not support times or recurrence in API v1

List of possible recurrence types which may/may not be supported in future:
- every Weekday
- every Mon/Tue/Wed/...
- every 2 weeks (on a particular day?)
- every month on the nth day
- every month on the nth Mon/Tue/Wed/...
- every month on the last but nth Mon/Tue/Wed/...
- every (n) year (s) on day/month

